ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ice-spice-denzel-washington@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ice-spice-denzel-washington@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ice-spice-denzel-washington@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">艾斯·斯佩斯</a>很快将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spike-lee">斯派克·李</a>即将上映的电影中与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-washington">丹泽尔·华盛顿</a>一起首次亮相。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/back-to-black-amy-winehouse-marisa-abela-3615314">《回归黑色》评论：玛丽莎·阿贝拉 (Marisa Abela) 成为了艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse) 的当之无愧的明星</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/ice-spice-cast-spike-lee-high-and-low-denzel-washington-1235966628/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em>报道</a>，艾斯·斯派斯已经开始拍摄这部电影的场景，不过她的角色细节目前还处于保密状态。这部电影名为<em>《High And Low》</em> ，是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/spike-lee-and-denzel-washington-reunite-to-remake-akira-kurosawa-crime-drama-3585059">对黑泽明 1963 年同名犯罪剧的英文翻拍和重新诠释</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3466104" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3466104" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3466104" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ice-spice-getty.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ice-spice-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ice-spice-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ice-spice-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ice-spice-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ice-spice-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ice-spice-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3466104" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Arturo Holmes/MG23/Getty Images for The Met Museum/Vogue</figcaption></figure><p>原版电影改编自艾德·麦克贝恩的小说《<em>国王的赎金</em>》，三船敏郎饰演一名富翁，被迫为雇员被绑架的儿子支付赎金。</p><p> <em>《High And Low》</em>的翻拍版将由 A24 在电影院上映，然后在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>上上映（据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/2024/feb/08/spike-lee-denzel-washington-akira-kurosawa-movie-remake" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道），不过电影上映和流媒体的上映日期尚未公布。</p><p>斯派克·李的《 <em>High And Low》</em>版本将标志着他与丹泽尔·华盛顿的第五次合作。他们过去的合作作品包括 1990 年的<em>Mo&#39; Better Blues</em> 、1992 年的<em>Malcom X</em> 、1998 年的<em>He Got Game</em>和 2006 年的<em>Inside Man</em> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3585093" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3585093" style="width: 1476px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3585093" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington.jpg" alt="" width="1476" height="1014" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington.jpg 1476w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-218x150.jpg 218w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-436x300.jpg 436w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-400x275.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-800x550.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-696x478.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-1392x956.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-1068x734.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1476px) 100vw, 1476px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3585093" class="wp-caption-text">斯派克·李和丹泽尔·华盛顿。图片来源：盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>在 Ice Spice 方面，这位说唱歌手将于今年某个时候发行她备受期待的首张专辑《Y2K》。据说唱歌手称，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-confirms-y2k-album-is-finished-3597276">这张专辑“已经完成”</a> ，并且<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-has-been-playing-album-at-full-volume-to-pass-the-car-test-3614999">最近“通过了汽车测试”</a> 。</p><p> 《Y2K》将接续这位布朗克斯说唱歌手 2023 年 1 月的 EP <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ice-spice-like-debut-project-review-bikini-bottom-radar-3383027#:~:text=Much%20like%20the%20sardonic%20vocals,project%2C%20such%20a%20sharp%20listen.">《Like..?》</a> ，其中包括《Munch (Feelin&#39; U)》和《In Ha Mood》等热门歌曲。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ice-spice-like-debut-project-review-bikini-bottom-radar-3383027#:~:text=Much%20like%20the%20sardonic%20vocals,project%2C%20such%20a%20sharp%20listen."><em>NME</em>授予该版本四颗星</a>，Thomas Smith 称赞 Ice Spice 的讽刺风格和冷静的自信。</p><p> “对于 Ice Spice 来说，路还很长，度过病毒爆发后的时期感觉至关重要：长寿感觉是可以实现的，但休闲听众甚至一些粉丝仍然善变，”史密斯写道。 “在‘​​喜欢……？’节目中，她似乎并不在意追逐影响力或粉丝——她知道无论如何他们最终都会回心转意。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ice-spice-to-star-alongside-denzel-washington-in-new-spike-lee-film-3616289">冰辣妹 (Ice Spice) 与丹泽尔·华盛顿 (Denzel Washington) 共同主演斯派克·李 (Spike Lee) 的新</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">电影</a></p>;
