w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·斯派尼和泰勒·斯威夫特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>卡莉·斯派尼 (Cailee Spaeny) 回忆起她最近遇见<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的</a>那一刻，并公开了他们是如何通过<em>《东镇母马》建立联系的。</em></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/mare-of-easttown-review-kate-winslet-2923609">《东镇的母马》评论：凯特·温斯莱特勇敢地面对小镇谋杀案的悲痛故事</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位演员曾在索菲亚·科波拉的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/priscilla-review-elvis-presley-sofia-coppola-3493033">《普里西拉》</a></em>中饰演普里西拉·普雷西，接下来将在亚历克斯·<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">加兰</a>的<em>《内战》</em>中出演银幕。凯特·温斯莱特，<em>东镇的母马。</em></p><p>该剧于 2021 年首播，讲述了一位小镇侦探（凯特·温斯莱特饰演的马雷）调查青少年艾琳·麦克梅纳明谋杀案的故事。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/kate-winslet-celebrates-middle-aged-imperfect-mare-of-easttown-character-emmys-2021-3049601">温丝莱特随后凭借表演赢得 2021 年艾美奖限定剧、选集系列或电影女主角奖</a>。</p><p> “泰勒·斯威夫特说她很喜欢<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">《东镇的马雷》</em> ，这太疯狂了，鲁比说，‘我也喜欢<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">《东镇的马雷</em>》！’” <em><a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/cailee-spaeny-talks-civil-war-taylor-swift-1235870573/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">斯佩尼</a></em>回忆道。</p><p>她继续说道：“然后泰勒说，‘但是你在<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">《伊斯特敦的母马》</em>中是金发女郎，不是吗？’所以我不知道泰勒说了什么。也许只是因为她是<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">东镇母马的</em>忠实粉丝，这非常酷。” </p><figure id="attachment_3020166" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3020166" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3020166" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one.jpg" alt="东镇母马" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3020166" class="wp-caption-text">凯特·温斯莱特和埃文·彼得斯在《东镇之海》中 图片来源：Sarah Shatz / HBO / 好莱坞档案馆</figcaption></figure><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">泰勒·斯威夫特 - “1989（泰勒版）”评论：她最好的专辑永远不会过时</a></strong></li></ul><p>温斯莱特此前曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/mare-of-easttown-season-2-kate-winslet-creator-some-very-cool-ideas-3012184">谈到<em>《伊斯特镇的母马》</em>回归第二季的可能性</a>，并表示该剧的创作者布拉德·英格尔斯比对于下一步的发展有“一些非常酷的想法”。 “布拉德创造性地分享了一些非常酷的想法。我们会看看会发生什么，”她说。</p><p> “我还必须弄清楚我是否能做到。我可以再经历一遍吗？成为她确实让我在情感上付出了很大的代价，我必须弄清楚我是否可以再次振作起来并再次做到这一点。”</p><p> 《东镇的母马》被<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/nme-best-tv-shows-of-the-year-2021-3113636"><em>NME</em>评为 2021 年十大电视节目</a>之一，并获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/mare-of-easttown-review-kate-winslet-2923609">四星评价</a>：“脾气暴躁、乐观向上、在经历了多年的悲剧后遭到打击的希恩是温丝莱特迄今为止最阴郁的角色之一。她也是她最优秀的人之一。随着剧情慢慢展开（她也面临失去小孙子的监护权），马雷吸着电子烟，她拥有一种在男性主导的工作中生存所需的特殊韧性，她的每一个决定都受到严格审查。比男同事的还要多。</p><p> “来感受小镇的神秘，既扣人心弦又令人沮丧。留下真实银幕传奇人物的磁性表演，”我们的评论总结道。</p><p>与此同时，继 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>获奖作品<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-midnights-review-3332805">《Midnights》</a>之后，斯威夫特将于下周五（4 月 19 日）发行她的第 11 张录音室唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">《The Tortured Poets Department》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cailee-spaeny-says-taylor-swift-is-a-huge-fan-of-mare-of-easttown-3616103">Cailee Spaeny 称泰勒·斯威夫特是《Mare Of Easttown》的超级粉丝的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
